wow The setting  Rockefeller center somewhere in the back  Empire State Building in the front with the lights going off  and to the left  hidden by the trees the Chrysler building  right by the fountain  People are here with friends and only one person  G themselves  It’s truly something  Just take a minute and look up  look how the lights shine for you  This is the o oh slciyh in the world    maybe Dubai    maybe Paris    maybe London  where the lights on all night shouldn’t be a crime  Everywhere else  it’s a crime  I love this city  This  This freedom of walking in a city at 10pm is what I am going to miss  Everything else I can get in Bangalore and more  But this  this feeling I log walking aimlessly until I figure it out is what I am going to miss  The constant activity brings you safety  I don’t even know what else to say but it’s this absolute utter beautiful feeling of freedom that I absolutely love and am going to miss 

