The narratives that we tell ourselves in exchange for the fear of living life and feeling emotions  
All I ve ever wanted is a community of people that support and love my endeavors  
I am so caught up in things of elsewhere   the past  another place  another time  another scenario that I forget to exist in the now  the present  
I don t have people around me who have the mindset that I am in currently   need to find that  
My room is still a heaping blazing disaster zone  
