Not showing up  Isn t friendship about showing up  About putting aside this anxiety  I am in a rut and I can never get out of it  I feel like I am choosing myself but I m hiding  Isn t it courage to go  To show  To risk  Isn t that what life is    the people you meet and the stories you accumulate 
I ve wanted to die for so long that I m glad to live today  To know that I ve made it to an age I didn t think I would  to acknowledge the greed and pain and sadness that I had in life  That it wasn t a part of my imagination  To have the knowledge that I will experience all of it again maybe worse but I will have more control 
