I was shook because I was giving the impression that I had no family trauma  How is it so easy for someone to diminish another s trauma  I don t talk about the trauma because I don t see the point in talking about it  It s easier to talk about the good things because the bad is horrible 
Looking at photos of myself as a child I am always struck by how I used to smile  But in some photos  I look at them and am transported back to how I was feeling  Was it then   when I was 7   that I stopped being happy  The expression in this undiscovered photo says it all  
